# Live Translation App - Dual Platform System

A real-time translation application with Chrome Extension and Web App, featuring Web3 authentication and crypto payments.

## Features

- 🌐 **Dual Platform**: Chrome Extension + Responsive Web App
- 🔐 **Web3 Authentication**: Sign-In with Ethereum (SIWE) + Google OAuth
- 💰 **Crypto Payments**: Accept USDC, BTC, ETH via Stripe Crypto
- 🔄 **Real-time Sync**: Supabase Realtime for instant state synchronization
- 📦 **Monorepo**: Turborepo-powered TypeScript monorepo

## Architecture

```
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                    CLIENT LAYER                              │
│  ┌─────────────────┐         ┌─────────────────────────┐    │
│  │ Chrome Extension│         │      Web Application    │    │
│  │  (Manifest V3)  │         │    (React + Vite)       │    │
│  └─────────────────┘         └─────────────────────────┘    │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
                            │
                            ▼
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                   SHARED LIBRARIES                           │
│  @lib/ui │ @lib/supabase │ @lib/web3 │ @lib/types          │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
                            │
                            ▼
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                    SUPABASE                                  │
│  Auth (SIWE + OAuth) │ Database │ Realtime │ Edge Functions │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
                            │
                            ▼
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                    STRIPE                                    │
│  Credit Cards │ Crypto (USDC/BTC/ETH) │ Subscriptions       │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

## Quick Start

### Prerequisites

- Node.js 18+
- pnpm 8+
- Supabase CLI
- MetaMask or compatible Web3 wallet

### Installation

```bash
# Clone repository
git clone https://github.com/your-org/live-translation-app.git
cd live-translation-app

# Install dependencies
pnpm install

# Copy environment variables
cp .env.example .env
# Edit .env with your Supabase and Stripe credentials

# Start Supabase locally (optional)
supabase start

# Run database migrations
pnpm db:migrate

# Start development servers
pnpm dev
```

### Development

```bash
# Run all apps in development mode
pnpm dev

# Run specific app
pnpm dev:web      # Web app only
pnpm dev:extension # Chrome extension only

# Type checking
pnpm typecheck

# Linting
pnpm lint

# Testing
pnpm test
```

